title: ASU dominates Colorado: Storylines and takeaways
text:
ASU dominates Colorado: Storylines and takeaways Arizona State continued to build momentum with their win over Colorado on Saturday. Post to Facebook ASU dominates Colorado: Storylines and takeaways Arizona State continued to build momentum with their win over Colorado on Saturday.   12news.com: http://12ne.ws/1RADRBU   Join the Conversation To   ASU dominates Colorado: Storylines and takeaways Robby Baker , 12 Sports 10:38 p.m. MST October 10, 2015 Arizona State continued to build momentum with their win over Colorado on Saturday. Oct 10, 2015; Tempe, AZ, USA; Arizona State Sun Devils tight end Kody Kohl (83) scores a touchdown after a fumble recovery against the Colorado Buffaloes during the first half at Sun Devil Stadium. Mandatory Credit: Joe Camporeale-USA TODAY Sports (Photo: Joe Camporeale-USA TODAY Sports) 
The ASU Sun Devils beat the Colorado Buffalos 48-23 on Saturday. 
Takin' care of business 
This is what ASU fans expected to see weeks two and three when the Sun Devils took on Cal Poly and New Mexico. 
Arizona State took care of business. 
The Sun Devils were clicking on all cylinders Saturday, and avoided falling in a 'trap game'. It would have been very easy for Todd Graham and company to get too high on themselves following their win over UCLA, but they didn't. 
It would have also been easy for ASU to be looking ahead to their impending matchup with the upstart Utah Utes.
